    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Firearms, usually shotguns, used in skeet shooting; normally autoloaders with more weight toward the front end of the gun than in field guns.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
